He had trouble with the zipper getting stuck.
Make sure the zipper is fully closed before washing.

zipper (zip fastener).definition: A fastening device consisting of two flexible strips with interlocking metal or plastic teeth.
examples: She pulled the zipper up on her jacket.
The bag has a sturdy zipper that keeps it closed.
He struggled to fix the broken zipper on his pants.
